### Core API

### 1. Get Alertmanager Status
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/status
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get All Receivers
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/receivers
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get All Alert groups
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/alerts/groups
Accept: application/json

### 4. Silence
### 4.1 Get All Silences
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/silences
Accept: application/json

### 4.2 Create Silence
POST {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/silences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matchers": [
    {
      "name": "alertname",
      "value": "HighCPU",
      "isRegex": false
    }
  ],
  "startsAt": "2025-10-19T16:40:00Z",
  "endsAt": "2025-10-20T01:00:00Z",
  "comment": "Maintenance window",
  "createdBy": "admin"
}

### 4.3 Get Specific Silence (replace {silenceId} with actual ID)
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/silence/{{silenceId}}
Accept: application/json

### 4.4 Delete Silence (replace {silenceId} with actual ID)
DELETE {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/silence/{{silenceId}}

### 5. Alerts
### 5.1
GET {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/alerts
Accept: application/json

### 5.2 Post Alerts (for testing)
POST {{PROMETHEUS_ALERTMANAGER_HOST}}/api/v2/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "labels": {
      "alertname": "TestAlert",
      "instance": "localhost:9090",
      "severity": "warning"
    },
    "annotations": {
      "summary": "Test alert for API testing",
      "description": "This is a test alert sent via API"
    },
    "startsAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endsAt": "2025-01-01T01:00:00Z"
  }
]

